name: Leather Luggage Tags
description:
For the busy traveler....for the active mom... for the sports enthusiast....for anyone with a bold sense of style.....
Tagasaurus Bag Tags!

These tags look great with almost any bag out there and makes a perfect gift. Use them on diaper bags, childrens items, suitcases, craft bags or any bag that needs to stand out and scream style! 

Tagasaurus™ Bag Tags are made with high quality leather, hand stitched for maximum, long-lasting durability against wear and tear. Each bag tag is approx. 4 1/2 inches and is sure to stand out on any luggage carousel, shelf, or bag rack.
All Tagasaurus™ Bag Tags come with adjustable black leather strap with chrome buckle and removable identification card insert in protective plastic packaging.
